---
// Gifts.astro
---

<section class="py-24 bg-[var(--color-bg-overlay-dark)] relative">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <div class="mb-10 flex justify-center text-[#C5A880]">
            <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="1"
                stroke="currentColor"
                class="w-16 h-16"
            >
                <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M21 11.25v8.25a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5H5.25a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5-1.5v-8.25M12 4.875A2.625 2.625 0 1 0 9.375 7.5H12m0-2.625V7.5m0-2.625A2.625 2.625 0 1 1 14.625 7.5H12m0 0V21m-8.625-9.75h18c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125v-1.5c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125h-18c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v1.5c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125Z"
                ></path>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-playfair text-4xl md:text-5xl text-text-main mb-6">
            Mesa de Regalos
        </h2>
        <p
            class="font-inter text-text-main/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed"
        >
            El mejor regalo es tu presencia, pero si deseas tener un detalle
            conmigo, puedes hacerlo a través de la siguiente cuenta:
        </p>

        <div
            class="reveal-card slide-from-right bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[5px] border border-white/20 shadow-xl w-full mx-auto text-left block relative"
        >
            <div class="mb-6">
                <p
                    class="font-inter text-xs tracking-widest text-[#C5A880] uppercase mb-1"
                >
                    Banco
                </p>
                <p class="font-inter text-text-main font-medium">
                    BBVA Bancomer
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-6">
                <p
                    class="font-inter text-xs tracking-widest text-[#C5A880] uppercase mb-1"
                >
                    Nombre
                </p>
                <p class="font-inter text-text-main font-medium">
                    Valentina García López
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p
                    class="font-inter text-xs tracking-widest text-[#C5A880] uppercase mb-1"
                >
                    CLABE INTERBANCARIA
                </p>
                <div
                    class="flex items-center justify-between bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 border border-white/30 rounded"
                >
                    <p class="font-mono text-text-main tracking-wider">
                        012 345 6789 0123 4567
                    </p>
                    <button
                        class="text-[#C5A880] hover:text-[#a38a65] transition-colors"
                        title="Copiar"
                        onclick="alert('CLABE copiada!');"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            class="w-5 h-5"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                d="M15.75 17.25v3.375c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-9.75a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V7.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H6.75a9.06 9.06 0 0 1 1.5.124m7.5 10.376h3.375c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25c0-4.46-3.243-8.161-7.5-8.876a9.06 9.06 0 0 0-1.5-.124H9.375c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v3.5m7.5 10.375H9.375a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125v-9.25m12 6.625v-1.875a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375h-1.5a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375H9.75"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
